PrecisEnactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 26 - which declares the severe flooding in north-central Alberta which occurred in late April, 1997, to be of concern to the federal government, and authorizes the provision of financial assistance in respect thereof.

precis:
Enactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 26 -
which declares the severe flooding in north-central Alberta which occurred
in late April, 1997, to be of concern to the federal government, and
authorizes the provision of financial assistance in respect thereof.
